title: Naughty and Nice
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small English bistro and ice cream parlour has a few vegetarian choices for lunch in an area with no specific vegetarian places to eat. The Homity Pie lunch plate consists of couscous and raisin salad, coleslaw, pasta and peppers salad, leaves, carrot and beetroot salad.
